function PrayerPage({d,s}){const[sh,setSh]=useState(false);const[tab,setTab]=useState("active");const[fm,setFm]=useState({text:"",by:""});const list=d.prayers.filter(p=>p.status===tab);return(<div className="space-y-4"><div className="flex gap-2"><Bt onClick={()=>{setFm({text:"",by:""});setSh(true)}}><Plus size={16}/></Bt><button onClick={()=>setTab("active")} className={"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium "+(tab==="active"?"bg-orange-500 text-white":"bg-gray-100")}>Active ({d.prayers.filter(p=>p.status==="active").length})</button><button onClick={()=>setTab("answered")} className={"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium "+(tab==="answered"?"bg-orange-500 text-white":"bg-gray-100")}>Answered</button></div>{list.map(p=>(<div key={p.id} className="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border"><div className="flex justify-between items-start"><div><div className="text-sm">{p.text}</div><div className="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">{p.by&&p.by+" · "}{fs(p.date)}</div></div><div className="flex gap-1"><button onClick={()=>s({...d,prayers:d.prayers.map(x=>x.id===p.id?{...x,status:x.status==="active"?"answered":"active",answeredDate:td()}:x)})} className="p-1 hover:bg-green-50 text-green-600"><Check size={14}/></button><button onClick={()=>s({...d,prayers:d.prayers.filter(x=>x.id!==p.id)})} className="p-1 hover:bg-red-50 text-red-400"><Trash2 size={14}/></button></div></div></div>))}{!list.length&&<div className="text-center text-gray-400 py-8">No {tab} prayers</div>}<M open={sh} onClose={()=>setSh(false)} title="Add Prayer"><Fl l="Request"><Ta value={fm.text} onChange={e=>setFm({...fm,text:e.target.value})}/></Fl><Fl l="By"><Ip value={fm.by} onChange={e=>setFm({...fm,by:e.target.value})}/></Fl><Bt onClick={()=>{if(!fm.text)return;s({...d,prayers:[...d.prayers,{...fm,id:gi(),date:td(),status:"active",answeredDate:""}]});setSh(false)}}><Check size={16}/>Submit</Bt></M></div>)}

